title: AFSCME Local 2985 to donate to Patriot Guard Riders
text:
Published By: Iowa City Press - Today 
AFSCME Local 2985 announces that it will present a $1,100 donation from their memorial fund to the Patriot Guard Riders at 10 a.m. Wednesday...
